title: KeenRush is now 17
content:
Well, it's now here the day I turn(ed) 17 years, 8th June..

Wish me happy birthday if you want. [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-smile.gif[/img]

[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-birthday.gif[/img] Yay, it's going to be fun today! Probably cat wakes me up ~6:03 am, I have to clean my room and some other rooms, I don't have any party, nothing good to eat, I'll be getting my present later (I haven't asked anything so they didn't buy anything, ".. first decide what you want .."), I haven't got any birthday greetings via snail-mail (or e-mail)..[list goes on and on].. [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-dead.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-yawn.gif[/img]

Oh, did I mention that I feel annoyingly old? I still haven't managed to do anything I could be truly proud of.. Annoying, all those young and gifted persons all over the net.. [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-garg.gif[/img] [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-oldy.gif[/img] We want Keen Chronicles!
